770
01:01:13,736 --> 01:01:14,736
Yu Sub.

771
01:01:16,106 --> 01:01:17,975
What are you doing here? It's not even the weekend.

772
01:01:18,705 --> 01:01:21,006
I was supposed to meet someone here, but I don't think they came.

773
01:01:21,345 --> 01:01:23,646
- What about you? - I'm here to meet someone too.

774
01:01:24,146 --> 01:01:26,816
- Do you want to go in together? - It's okay. It's stuffy inside.

775
01:01:27,216 --> 01:01:29,285
If you're going to be done soon, I'll wait outside.

776
01:01:29,416 --> 01:01:30,855
- Will you? - Sure.

777
01:01:30,856 --> 01:01:32,225
I'd love that.

778
01:01:35,896 --> 01:01:37,995
Gosh, your hat is so cool.

779
01:01:47,905 --> 01:01:49,635
Here you go.

780
01:01:50,606 --> 01:01:51,606
Let me see.

781
01:01:51,876 --> 01:01:53,376
Goodness, it looks good on you.

782
01:01:53,975 --> 01:01:55,745
It looks better on me, doesn't it?

783
01:01:57,345 --> 01:01:59,146
- Make it quick. - Okay, Yu Sub.

784
01:02:48,966 --> 01:02:50,736
(My Perfect Stranger)

785
01:02:50,865 --> 01:02:52,865
There's nothing about Baek Yu Sub.

786
01:02:52,966 --> 01:02:54,776
None of these files have any information.

787
01:02:54,876 --> 01:02:57,135
No one knows Baek Yu Sub better than me.

788
01:02:57,176 --> 01:02:59,106
I'll give you everything you need.

789
01:02:59,146 --> 01:03:01,005
If Baek Yu Sub is the culprit,

790
01:03:01,006 --> 01:03:02,844
we're going to see him again tomorrow night...

791
01:03:02,845 --> 01:03:05,046
because he needs to kill the second victim.

792
01:03:05,285 --> 01:03:07,085
Where in the world could he be?

793
01:03:07,086 --> 01:03:09,115
- We looked everywhere... - It won't happen anytime soon.

794
01:03:09,385 --> 01:03:10,385
Hello?

795
01:03:32,146 --> 01:03:35,646
(My Perfect Stranger)
